CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 1, 1967, pg. 13, reads: "Hosted Regional - These members represent Kappa Chapter of Chi Eta Phi Sorority which entertained the North East Regional Conference. Left to right: Sorors Elsie Murray, Carrie Bullock, Dorothy Gambrell, Joyce Lomax, Mamie Garland and Marie Cowans."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Chi Eta Phi sorority members, from left: Elsie Murray, Carrie Bullock, Dorothy Gambrell, Joyce Lomax, Mamie Garland, and Marie Cowans, gathered behind table with Chi Eta Phi sorority plaque with medical symbol, in Howard Johnsons for sorority conference
